column1: #Text=The Los Angeles Clippers defeated the host Charlotte Hornets , 124 - 121 , at Staples Center on Wednesday .
#Text=The Clippers ( 36 - 23 ) came into this game as a big favorite and they left it once again on Friday .
#Text=Blake Griffin led the way for the Clippers with 43 points on 15 - of - 26 shooting , including 3 - of - 4 from long range , including 3 - of - 4 from three - point range .
#Text=Jordan added 19 rebounds , one assist , three steals and two blocks , in 43 minutes .
#Text=JJ Redick chipped in 22 points on 9 - of - 16 shooting , including 3 - of - 7 from long range , along with two rebounds , five assists and one steal .
#Text=JJ Redick added 22 points , two rebounds and two assists , and Frank Kaminsky chipped in 16 points on 5 - of - 13 shooting , to go with five rebounds and four assists .
